               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18200628-56-person562">
                  THOMAS 
                  CRIBB
               <interp inst="t18200628-56-person562" type="surname" value="CRIBB"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200628-56-person562" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200628-56-person562" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am servant to Mr. Castle. On the 27th of May I saw the prisoner coming out of the counting-house with this coat. As soon as he saw me he dropped it. I walked up to him, and asked what he was going to do with it? he said some strange man, with a knot on his head, sent him for it. I ordered him to take it up and put it where he found it. He put it on a chair in the counting-house, where I had seen it before - I then gave him in charge.</p>
